<!-- SECTION 5: SOP GEOMETRY -->
<section class="hidden" id="sop">
<h2>SOP Geometry</h2>
<p>Surface OPerators handle 3D geometry: mesh generation, deformation, particle systems, and import/export. SOPs connect to render pipelines via MAT operators and Render TOPs. TD's Python-scriptable SOP pipeline enables generative and data-driven geometry.</p>
<div class="canvas-wrap">
