</div>
<div style="margin-top:1rem">
<span class="node-badge node-sop">Sphere SOP</span> →
    <span class="node-badge node-sop">Noise SOP</span> →
    <span class="node-badge node-sop">Point SOP</span> →
    <span class="node-badge node-mat">PBR MAT</span> →
    <span class="node-badge node-top">Render TOP</span>
</div>
<div class="card-grid">
<div class="card"><h3>Particle SOP</h3><p>GPU-accelerated particle system. Forces, constraints, and per-particle attributes. Connect to Point Instancer for mass geometry instancing.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Noise SOP</h3><p>Displaces geometry vertices along noise field. Animating offset produces organic deformation. Frequency and amplitude control sculpt the effect.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Line MAT</h3><p>Wire-frame rendering of SOP geometry. Essential for skeletal data visualization, particle trails, and minimalist aesthetic performances.</p></div>
<div class="card"><h3>Point Instancer SOP</h3><p>Places geometry instances at each point. Combine with Noise SOP to create organic particle fields. Render millions of instances in real time.</p></div>
</div>
</section>
